│ case; the pass incorrectly concludes all cases are covered and replaces the default with unreachable. A safe    │
│ fix is to only mark the default unreachable when the condition is known to be a single exact constant (i.e.,    │
│ the constant range is a single element), ensuring it must match one of the case constants handled earlier. I    │
│ will update the condition to require CR.isSingleElement() before making the default unreachable.                │
